In drawings that illustrate the present invention by way of example:


FIG. 1 is an exploded view of a knee prosthesis according to the present invention;


FIG. 2 is a top view of the femoral component of FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 is a sectional view, through a condyle, of the component of FIG. 2, showing bone cut pattern;


FIG. 3A is a view similar to FIG. 3, showing the orientation of a prior art femoral component to the longitudinal axis of the femur;


FIG. 3B is a view similar to FIG. 3, showing an alternative embodiment of the femoral component of the present invention;


FIG. 4 is a schematic view of the distal end of a femur, showing bone cut lines, relative to the trans-epicondylar line of the femur; and


FIGS. 5 and 5A are cross-sectional view of patellar lining components of the present invention, which are overall anatomically shaped.
